#: ../../../manual/cmake-instrumentation.7.rst:715
msgid ""
"The JSON format is described in machine-readable form by :download:`this "
"JSON schema </manual/instrumentation/index-v1-schema.json>`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../manual/cmake-instrumentation.7.rst:722
msgid "v1 CMake Content File"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../manual/cmake-instrumentation.7.rst:724
msgid ""
"CMake content files contain information about the CMake configure and "
"generate steps. Each `v1 Snippet File`_ provides the path to one of these "
"files corresponding to the CMake invocation responsible for generating its "
"command."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../manual/cmake-instrumentation.7.rst:728
msgid "Each CMake content file contains the following:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../manual/cmake-instrumentation.7.rst:731
msgid ""
"The `Data Version`_ of the content file, written as ``{ \"major\": 1, "
"\"minor\": N }`` where ``N`` is the most recent minor version."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../manual/cmake-instrumentation.7.rst:734
msgid "``project``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../manual/cmake-instrumentation.7.rst:735
msgid "The value of :variable:`CMAKE_PROJECT_NAME`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../manual/cmake-instrumentation.7.rst:738
msgid ""
"An object containing arbitrary JSON data specified by the user with the :ref:"
"`cmake_instrumentation CUSTOM_CONTENT` functionality of the :command:"
"`cmake_instrumentation` command."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../manual/cmake-instrumentation.7.rst:742
msgid "``targets``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../manual/cmake-instrumentation.7.rst:743
msgid ""
"An object containing CMake targets, indexed by name, that have corresponding "
"instrumentation data. Each target contains the following:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../manual/cmake-instrumentation.7.rst:746
msgid "``type``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../manual/cmake-instrumentation.7.rst:747
msgid ""
"The :prop_tgt:`TYPE` property of the target. Only ``EXECUTABLE``, "
"``STATIC_LIBRARY``, ``SHARED_LIBRARY``, ``MODULE_LIBRARY`` and "
"``OBJECT_LIBRARY`` targets are included."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../manual/cmake-instrumentation.7.rst:751
msgid "``labels``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../manual/cmake-instrumentation.7.rst:752
msgid "The :prop_tgt:`LABELS` property of the target."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../manual/cmake-instrumentation.7.rst:757
msgid "Google Trace File"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../manual/cmake-instrumentation.7.rst:759
msgid ""
"CMake can generate a file in the `Google Trace Event Format`_ to help "
"visualize collected instrumentation data. Enabling the ``trace`` option in "
"the `v1 Query Files`_ causes such a file to be generated under ``<build>/."
"cmake/instrumentation/v1/data/trace`` whenever `Indexing`_ occurs."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../manual/cmake-instrumentation.7.rst:764
msgid ""
"Generated trace files include data from all `v1 Snippet Files <v1 Snippet "
"File_>`_ listed in the current index file."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../manual/cmake-instrumentation.7.rst:767
msgid ""
"When instrumentation data is deleted by CMake after `Indexing`_, the most "
"recent trace file remains so that it can be manually inspected without the "
"need for any custom `Callbacks`_."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../manual/cmake-instrumentation.7.rst:771
msgid ""
"Trace files are stored in the ``JSON Array Format``, where each `v1 Snippet "
"File`_ corresponds to a single trace event object. Each trace event contains "
"the following data:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../manual/cmake-instrumentation.7.rst:775
msgid "``name``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../manual/cmake-instrumentation.7.rst:776
msgid "A descriptive name generated by CMake based on the given snippet data."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../manual/cmake-instrumentation.7.rst:778
msgid "``cat``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../manual/cmake-instrumentation.7.rst:779
msgid "The ``role`` from the `v1 Snippet File`_."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../manual/cmake-instrumentation.7.rst:781
msgid "``ph``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../manual/cmake-instrumentation.7.rst:782
msgid "Currently, always ``\"X\"`` to represent \"Complete Events\"."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../manual/cmake-instrumentation.7.rst:784
msgid "``ts``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../manual/cmake-instrumentation.7.rst:785
msgid ""
"The ``timeStart`` from the `v1 Snippet File`_, converted from milliseconds "
"to microseconds."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../manual/cmake-instrumentation.7.rst:788
msgid "``dur``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../manual/cmake-instrumentation.7.rst:789
msgid ""
"The ``duration`` from the `v1 Snippet File`_, converted from milliseconds to "
"microseconds."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../manual/cmake-instrumentation.7.rst:792
msgid "``pid``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../manual/cmake-instrumentation.7.rst:793
msgid "Unused (always zero)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../manual/cmake-instrumentation.7.rst:795
msgid "``tid``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../manual/cmake-instrumentation.7.rst:796
msgid ""
"An integer ranging from zero to the number of concurrent jobs with which the "
"processes being indexed ran. This is a synthetic ID calculated by CMake "
"based on the ``ts`` and ``dur`` of all snippet files being indexed in order "
